highlights.text: “I Hate U” by SZA is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #19.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 253 weeks straight.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Blinding Lights” is the highest at #34.
“Infinity” by Jaymes Young is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 53 spots at #53.
